            <a class="anchor-light">Meer informatie</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-3">
        <div>
            <h1>Kunstenaars</h1>
            <p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Sed at rhoncus tortor. Donec rhoncus mi ac laoreet feugiat. Nam massa ligula, lacinia non viverra sit amet, ultrices at nunc.</p>
            <div>
                <a class="anchor-dark">Bekijk alle kunstennaars</a>&nbsp;
                <a class="anchor-dark">Bekijk collectie</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div>
            <div>
                <img src="/assets/kunstenaars/peter-jacquemyn/profiel.png"/>
                <h2>Peter Jacquemyn</h2>
                <a class="anchor-dark">Meer informatie</a>
            </div>
            <div>
                <img src="/assets/kunstenaars/pal-horvath/profiel.png"/>
                <h2>Pal Horvath</h2>
                <a class="anchor-dark">Meer informatie</a>
            </div>
            <div>
                <img src="/assets/kunstenaars/valerie-de-smedt/profiel.png"/>
                <h2>Valerie De Smedt</h2>
                <a class="anchor-dark">Meer informatie</a>
            </div>
            <div>
                <img src="/assets/kunstenaars/eric-leon/profiel.png"/>
                <h2>Eric Leon</h2>
                <a class="anchor-dark">Meer informatie</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="section-4">
        <div>
            <p>Contact</p>
            <h1>Vragen over onze diensten? Interesse in een kunstwerk?</h1>
            <a class="anchor-dark">Contacteer ons</a>
        </div>
        <div>
            <img src="/assets/index-4.png" />
        </div>
        <div>
            <img src="/assets/index-5.png" />
        </div>
        <div>
            <h1>Art-line is een kunstgallerij in hartje Dilbeek.</h1>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>

<style>
    .section-1 {
        padding: 2.5em 5em;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(12, 1fr);
        grid-template-rows: repeat(6, 1fr);
    }

    .section-1 > :nth-child(1) {
        grid-column-start: 2;
        grid-column-end: 7;
        grid-row-start: 1;
        grid-row-end: 4;
    }

    .section-1 > :nth-child(2) {
        grid-column-start: 8;
        grid-column-end: 13;
        grid-row-start: 1;
        grid-row-end: 3;
    }

    .section-1 > :nth-child(3) {
        grid-column-start: 8;
        grid-column-end: 13;
        grid-row-start: 3;
        grid-row-end: 6;
    }

    .section-1 > :nth-child(4) {
        grid-column-start: 1;
        grid-column-end: 5;
        grid-row-start: 4;
        grid-row-end: 7;
    }

    .section-1 > :nth-child(5) {
        margin-top: auto;
        grid-column-start: 6;
        grid-column-end: 13;
        grid-row-start: 6;
        grid-row-end: 7;
    }

    .aside {
        padding-left: 2.5em;
        margin: 2.5em 0;
        border-left: 2px solid var(--white);
        line-height: 1;
    }
    .section-2 {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 5em;
        padding: 5em;
        margin: 2.5em 5em;
        background-color: var(--accent-3);
        color: var(--white);
    }

    .section-2 > :nth-child(2) {
        margin: auto 0;
    }

    .section-3 {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 2.5em;
        align-items: center;
        padding: 2.5em 5em;
    }

    .section-3 > :nth-child(1) {
        text-align: center;
        width: 25em;
    }

    .section-3 > :nth-child(2) {
        display: grid;
        width: 100%;
        gap: 2.5em;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    }

    .section-4 {
        padding: 5em;
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 6fr 1fr 5fr;
        grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
    }

    .section-4 > :nth-child(1) {
        text-align: right;
    }

    .section-4 > :nth-child(2) {
        grid-column-start: 3;
        grid-column-end: 4;
        grid-row-start: 1;
        grid-row-end: 3;
    }

    .section-4 > :nth-child(3) {
        grid-column-start: 1;
        grid-column-end: 2;
        grid-row-start: 2;
        grid-row-end: 4;
    }
    
    .section-4 > :nth-child(4) {
        margin-top: auto;
        
        grid-column-start: 3;
        grid-column-end: 4;
        grid-row-start: 3;
        grid-row-end: 4;1
    }

    img {
        width: 100%;
    }
</style>
